# Layouts

## What is contained within this directory? 

This directory stores the layouts of the main page of the site, stored in the HAML markup language.

## application.html.haml

This file is the main page of the site, notably missing many elements of the prompt builder, as they are added in from javascript files.

## mailer.html and mailer.text.haml

These files contain the layout of the mailer form.